reviewText: It really enjoyed it.was really awesome thank you amazon.com
it was in great condition and made love wrestling even more

This is a product that was explained as a Collector's Edition, which it is. But, it happens to be for a specific Wrestlemania. Wrestlemania 22. Had I know this it would have affected my purchasing decision. Products whether used or new need to be at least titled specific. Dissapointed with this option. The product itself was decent though.
